@startuml
' Communication diagram with numbered messages
object "User" as U
object "Web UI" as UI
object "Backend API" as API
object "F1DataService" as S
object "FastF1 Library" as F

U  -> UI  : 1. select race & drivers
UI -> API : 2. GET /insights(request)
API -> S  : 3. buildInsights(request)
S  -> F   : 4. loadSessionData(season,race,session)
F  --> S  : 5. session data
S  --> API: 6. insight result (chart data)
API --> UI: 7. JSON response
UI --> U  : 8. render chart

@enduml
